{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8a981c1248","title":"视察四川省一个养猪场时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6b42d731e6","index":0,"year":1958,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"8a981c1248","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"054d15bb64","type":"title","text":"视察四川省一个养猪场时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"283aeb94e3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：（对饲养员）辛苦了，好同志！（握手）祝你们获得更天成功","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed0c9e2711","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员（以下简称饲）：全靠你老人家的教导！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8254ba6f43","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：主要是你们自己的努力","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb8070b932","type":"paragraph","text":"（对社长）能使你们全社妇女都当上模范吗","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e70d44c503","type":"paragraph","text":"社长：保证全能当上，毛主席！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b0a3249c7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：全当上模范未必行吧！只能在二三年内做到有一半妇女当上模范就不错了。你说我这个看法保守吗？（众笑）","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"93883f7d9b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：参观一下你们的养猪场好吗？","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c21fdc44e5","type":"paragraph","text":"饲：欢迎，欢迎！毛主席多指教！","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b16e6ab8f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：别什么都要我指教吧，我和口口都是来向你们学习的，在许多事情上，你们比我们内行多了，是吧","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7f1df2821","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这是什么？","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e3fcc14946","type":"paragraph","text":"饲：是糖化牛类，拿来喂猪的，猪很爱吃。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2a873392b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：真是新鲜事儿，牛粪也能喂猪！怎么个制法？介绍一下吧。（摸出日记本来作记录，向口口说）来，我们都记上吧，这是群众的创造！从前我们就没听见说过。看来我们中国那句老话“做到老，学到老”实在不错！","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f13a7fe42","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：（对一个回乡知识青年）回家喂猪有意见吗","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3a79ac31b5","type":"paragraph","text":"饲：有啥意见呀！我一辈子也不愿意离开这养猪场理！","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"22f743b2cd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：很好！可要把你学的科学，传授给群众才更好。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73044934bb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：多看看先进的东西，眼光就会更开阔些。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a54d491653","type":"paragraph","text":"（亲自给一头猪打了蛋清针，然后对口口口说）","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80054bb751","type":"paragraph","text":"这里的经验真不少，特别是代饲料，如果全国都推广，一年要节约好几十亿斤粮食理！请记者同志在报纸上介绍一下好吗？","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"943297592b","type":"paragraph","text":"口口口：办得到。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8be0367013","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：最好后天见报。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3948dd29d3","type":"paragraph","text":"（对饲养员）谢谢你们！对我们教育太大了！","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cda1a3f1e7","type":"paragraph","text":"饲：可有人看不起我们理！","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b944b1643","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：谁？谁是顽固派","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"13e5c87dc8","type":"paragraph","text":"（饲养员介绍一些人如何从轻视妇女到称赞妇女的成绩","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4f6ebfe92","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：看不起妇女的人虽不多，但哪里总有几个，这不完全怪他们，过去封建制度对他们影响太深了，脑筋一下不容易转过弯来，又不能用飞机大炮来对付他们。那怎么办呢？我看除了加强教育外，最好的办法，就是妇女同志们做出成绩来，多拿事实给他们看，看得多了，他们脑子里的那个“封建王国”就会不攻自破的。","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":195,"end":194}},"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"03091d89a6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：这是什么？","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"070ee37e6a","type":"paragraph","text":"（对饲养员）谢谢你们！对我们教育太大了！","index":21,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a8b40baf0","type":"paragraph","text":"（亲自给一头猪打了蛋清针，然后对××说）","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b5e58e06b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：主要是你们自己的努力。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1104c71e42","type":"title","text":"视察四川省一个养猪场时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"13ac0c4218","type":"paragraph","text":"（见《中国妇女》1958 年第 7 期）","index":26,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"26688a3d04","type":"paragraph","text":"×××：办得到。","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2829bb2561","type":"paragraph","text":"这里的经验真不少，特别是代饲料，如果全国都推广，一年要节约好几十亿斤粮食哩！请记者同志在报纸上介绍一下好吗？","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48ea1f5676","type":"paragraph","text":"（饲养员介绍一些人如何从轻视妇女到称赞妇女的成绩。）","index":24,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52981ad840","type":"paragraph","text":"饲养员：是糖化牛粪，拿来喂猪的，猪很爱吃。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"664670350f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：（对一个回乡知识青年）回家喂猪有意见吗？","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71c23f826a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：......多看看先进的东西，眼光就会更开阔些。","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c665060a0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：看不起妇女的人虽不多，但哪里总有几个，这不完全怪他们，过去封建制度对他们影响太深了，脑筋一下不容易转过弯来，又不能用飞机大炮来对付他们。那怎么办呢？我看除了加强教育外，最好的办法，就是妇女同志们做出成绩来，多拿事实给他们看，看得多了，他们脑子里的那个封建王国就会不攻自破的。","index":25,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86a55b87d2","type":"paragraph","text":"（对社长）能使你们全社妇女都当上模范吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"8a981c1248","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ea56b2f7e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：参观一下你们的养猪场好吗？","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui4","